data.description: Located in a gorgeous, gated community, at the base of beautiful South Mountain, this single level home is immaculate and inviting! The Tuscan stone and unique architecture with turret entry give this home such great curb appeal. Situated on a prime north/south facing lot next to the greenbelt & walking path, this open, split floorplan features 3 bedrooms, 2 baths and a den! It was one of the most desirable floor plans of the builder! Soaring vaulted ceilings give the great room and kitchen such an open feel! The kitchen is the focal point, with an eat at island bar, granite counters, all newer Frigidaire stainless steel appliances, including a French-door refrigerator, modern tile backsplash, 42-inch maple cabinets, pantry and the entire home was updated with a top-of-the-line Kinetico water filtration & softener system! The 20 ft. wall to wall panel, multi sliding glass doors take the great room to another level of elegance & comfort and connect the indoor and outdoor living spaces nicely! The master bedroom is spacious and off the great room area, with a tile & marble shower, raised vanity w/double sinks, private toilet and large master closet! The front area of the home features 2 additional bedrooms and an open den, with a built-in desk. The 2nd bathroom has a tub/shower and raised vanity w/double sinks! The laundry room is pre plumbed for a sink & includes a front-loading Samsung washer & dryer! You will simply love relaxing by the fountain in the peaceful backyard, with upgraded pavers, covered patio w/ceiling fans and lots of beautiful landscaping! (Fountain is functional and on a timer) The grill & fire pit are included! The entire home is faux wood tile and ceramic tile, which keeps you nice and cool in the Summer! All maintained & loved well by 1 owner! The gated community features a community pool, walking trails, tot lot and tree lined streets! Just minutes from walking trails, hiking, Downtown Phoenix, Sky Harbor Airport, Tempe, schools, dining and entertainment. The area is growing w/ the light rail expansion to Baseline coming in 2024! This home is simply wonderful! Come view it today! (Buyer to verify all information during due diligence period)
